Title: Landau Levels in the noncommutative $AdS_2$
Authors: R. Iengo (SISSA), R. Ramachandran (IMSc)
Comments: 19 pages, Latex, references and clarifications added including 2
  figures
Subj-class: High Energy Physics - Theory; Mathematical Physics; Mesoscopic
  Systems and Quantum Hall Effect
Journal-ref: JHEP 0202 (2002) 017
\\
  We formulate the Landau problem in the context of the noncommutative analog
of a surface of constant negative curvature, that is $AdS_2$ surface, and
obtain the spectrum and contrast the same with the Landau levels one finds in
the case of the commutative $AdS_2$ space.
